org.zyp.cn8583
类 cnValue<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.zyp.cn8583.cnValue<T>

public class cnValue<T>
extends java.lang.Object

这是一个中国版的8583格式标准的类，初始源代码来自于IsoValue。 Represents a value that is stored in a field inside a china 8583 message. It can format the value when the message is generated. Some values have a fixed length, other values require a length to be specified so that the value can be padded to the specified length. LLVAR and LLLVAR values do not need a length specification because the length is calculated from the stored value.

作者：
zyplanke

构造方法详细信息

cnValue

public cnValue(cnType t,
               T value)
Creates a new instance that stores the specified value as the specified type. Useful for storing LLVAR or LLLVAR types, as well as fixed-length value types like DATE10, DATE4, AMOUNT, etc.

参数：
t - the cnType.
value - The value to be stored.

cnValue

public cnValue(cnType t,
               T val,
               int len)
Creates a new instance that stores the specified value as the specified type. Useful for storing fixed-length value types.

方法详细信息

getType

public cnType getType()
Returns the cnType to which the value must be formatted.

getLength

public int getLength()
Returns the length of the stored value, of the length of the formatted value in case of NUMERIC or ALPHA. It doesn't include the field length header in case of LLVAR or LLLVAR.

getValue

public T getValue()
Returns the stored value without any conversion or formatting.

toString

public java.lang.String toString()
Returns the formatted value as a String. The formatting depends on the type of the receiver.
